sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Operator Controller<br/>redhat-ods-applications
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Engine<br/>In-Process
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Ollama as Ollama Server<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,HF: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Auth: kubeconfig
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch notification (in-process)
    Controller->>Kustomize: Render manifests (in-process)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, PVC<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>LlamaStack: Start Llama Stack pod
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update CR status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR status updated

    Note over User,HF: Flow 2: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Proxy: GET /metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Token valid
    Proxy->>Controller: Forward request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (internal)
    Controller-->>Proxy: Metrics response
    Proxy-->>Prometheus: Metrics (HTTPS)

    Note over User,HF: Flow 3: Llama Stack Inference Request
    User->>LlamaStack: POST /inference/chat_completion<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: None/Custom
    alt Ollama distribution
        LlamaStack->>Ollama: Forward inference request<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
        Ollama-->>LlamaStack: Inference response
    else vLLM distribution
        LlamaStack->>vLLM: Forward inference request<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: Optional Token
        Note over vLLM,HF: First request may download model
        vLLM->>HF: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: HF Token
        HF-->>vLLM: Model files
        vLLM-->>LlamaStack: Inference response
    end
    LlamaStack-->>User: JSON response

    Note over User,HF: Flow 4: ConfigMap Update and Pod Restart
    User->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>Auth: kubeconfig
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch notification (in-process)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Deployment annotations<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>LlamaStack: Rolling restart (new pods)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Reconciliation complete
